description: In this altered World War II, the Japanese make their attack a week early on Pearl Harbor while the American Volunteer Group (AVG), better known as the Flying Tigers, is also en route to bomb Japan and are recalled, only to secretly make another bombing attack on December 7th!
name: Flying Tigers

description: The Man of Steel Against The World's Mightiest Mortal!
name: When Earths Collide!

description: Visions of home-brewed hell take center stage as an anti-war protest on a California college campus turns into a cannibalistic massacre at the clawing hands of the hungry undead. Two lost soldiers fight their way across a jungle wasteland teeming with rot. And in Vietnam, Agent Declan Rule reveals his true reasons for being in country.
name: Beneath Blue Suburban Skies

description:
Prima Linea [Frontline]

First on-field mission for Gemini, the Anti-Terrorist Italian Team! Even without the Euromind approval! Even without the approval of the pubblic opinion! And against the terrorist group "Alba Dorata", which aim seem be... discover the terrible truth of the Gemini origins!

Il Filo della Morte [The Edge of Death]

In Italy, the Eurolab must save the passengers of a plane crashed into the sea. In Malaysia, the Task Force must investigate on another plane crash. Both seem related to some mutate creature... but the Lords of War dosen't want that they discover the truth!
name: Prima Linea / Il Filo Della Morte

description:
Seconda Chance [Second Chance]

Front know the truth about the origin of Gemini, and have killed his father! Suede, Balance, Grip and Mandala must capture them before he go even more insane. Mean while, Jorunalist Carlo Paci investigate on the dead of Edwig Caine. But who is the misterious drunken man hunted by horrible nightmare?

Principi Comuni [Shared Values]

With the Task Force nearly exterminated and Argento manifesting strange powers, the surviving members of both team must join the force an plan a mission to the Nadir Inc. base. But they dosen't know that the S.H.A.P.E. itself want them dead!
name: Seconda Chance / Principi Comuni

description:
Terza Posizione [Third Place]

While Front, horribly disfigured by Agent Lancelot, try to show evidence of the crime of his father to Journalist Carlo Paci, someone assault the Gemini Base of Vera Croce, and the team, alongside Agent Lancelot, must fight for their lives! And the misterious Voyager is coming to earth...

Nel Cuore della Bestia [In the Belly of the Beast]

Now joined in the Euroforce, the seven european heroes attack the Nadir Inc. for recover their teammate Iceboy. They don't say that their enemy is the terrible A.I.M., and that they are also chesed d by their own organizzation!
name: Terza Posizione / Nel Cuore Della Bestia

description:
Quarto Potere [Forth Power]

Curtain Fall! All the Truth! Gemini vs Gemini, Mr. Illusion and Alma Matrix vs all! Nosferath vs The Voyager! The horrible secret of their origins have been discovered, but now Gemini must fight for their soul, their future, and for save the whole planet!

Caso Chiuso [Case Closed]

The fate of Iceboy, the final battle with Nadir Inc. and A.I.M., and the secret plan of Francois Borillon! And no matter what, this will be the last battle for the Euroforce!
name: Quarto Potere / Caso Chiuso

description: It is 2021, tomorrow is the 20th anniversary of 9/11. America is under oppression by ultra-liberal extremists who have surrendered governing authority to the United Nations. Hate speech legislation called the “Coulter Laws” have forced vocal conservatives underground. A group of bio-mechanically enhanced conservatives led by Sean Hannity, G. Gordon Liddy, Oliver North, and a young man born on September 11, 2001, set out to thwart Ambassador Usama bin Laden's plans to nuke New York City.
name: Liberality For All, Part 1
